  "stem": "<p>In a right triangle, one of the non-right angles measures <math><mn>60</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math> and the length of the hypotenuse is <math><mn>12</mn></math>. What is the length of the side opposite the <math><mn>30</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math> angle?</p>",
