  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. In a 30-60-90 right triangle, the side opposite the 30° angle is half the length of the hypotenuse. So that side is 12/2 = 6.</p><p>Choice B is 12/3. Choice C is the side opposite 60°. Choice D is 12√3 (an unrelated multiple).</p>",
